OL,3,C'It's frightening': Abbott speaks of
OL,4,Csafety concerns after remarks by Tory
OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,FTory donor, Frank Hester, has
OL,8,Fapologised after reportedly saying
OL,9,FLabour MP Diane Abbott made him 'want
OL,10,Fto hate all black people' and that she
OL,11,Fshould be shot
OL,13,FMP Diane Abbott says comments about
OL,14,Fher by top Tory donor Frank Hester are
OL,15,F"frightening", after he reportedly
OL,16,Fsaid she made him "want to hate all
OL,17,Fblack women" and that "she should be
OL,18,Fshot".
