OL,5,Cdonor
OL,7,F"To hear someone talking like this is
OL,8,Fworrying", she said in a statement on
OL,9,FTuesday morning.
OL,11,F"I live in Hackney and do not drive so
OL,12,FI find myself, at week-ends, popping
OL,13,Fon a bus or even walking places more
OL,14,Fthan most MPs. I am a single woman and
OL,15,Fthat makes me vulnerable anyway"
OL,17,FShe also added: "For all of my career
OL,18,Fas an MP I have thought it important,
OL,19,Fnot to live in a bubble, but to mix
OL,20,Fand mingle with ordinary people.
