OL,7,F"The fact that two MPs have been
OL,8,Fmurdered in recent years makes talk
OL,9,Flike this all the more alarming.
OL,11,F"I am currently not a member of the
OL,12,FParliamentary Labour Party but remain
OL,13,Fa member of the Labour Party itself so
OL,14,FI am hoping for public support from
OL,15,FKeir Starmer."
OL,17,FMr Hester says he is "deeply sorry"
OL,18,Ffor his comments.
