OL,7,FThe chief executive of The Phoenix
OL,8,FPartnership (TPP), has admitted making
OL,9,F"rude" comments, but said they had
OL,10,F"nothing to do with her gender nor
OL,11,Fcolour of skin".
OL,13,FMr Hester issued a follow up statement
OL,14,Fon Tuesday afternoon saying "racism...
OL,15,Fis a poison that has no place in
OL,16,Fpublic life."
OL,18,F"We should have the confidence to
OL,19,Fdiscuss our differences openly and
OL,20,Feven playfully", he continued.
