OL,7,FGovernment minister Graham Stuart said
OL,8,FMr Hester shouldn't be "destroyed"
OL,9,Fover the comments, after they were
OL,10,Ffirst reported by , refusing to call
OL,11,Fthem racist, saying he was "not ready
OL,12,Fto put a label on it".
OL,14,F"Do we have to destroy this man
OL,15,Fbecause he said these unacceptable
OL,16,Fthings? I would hope not", he said.
