OL,7,FMr Stuart resisted calls for the
OL,8,FConservatives to return donations from
OL,9,FMr Hester: "These comments if true are
OL,10,Fpretty awful, but does that mean this
OL,11,Fperson has no value? Are we going to
OL,12,Fcancel him? He can't donate to a
OL,13,Fpolitical party?", he asked.
OL,15,FHe proceeded to speak at length about
OL,16,Fcancel culture and "tolerance".
