OL,7,FAdding: "It's funny, the people who
OL,8,Fpreach tolerance the most... seem
OL,9,Falways to be the least intolerant",
OL,10,Fbut Mr Stuart insisted: "I'm not
OL,11,Fremotely trying to justify this".
OL,13,F"If you went back through my life in
OL,14,Fevery private moment, and you took
OL,15,Fevery time I was furious about
OL,16,Fsomething in politics and took it out
OL,17,Fof context and put it on your
OL,18,Fprogramme now, I think I'd be
OL,19,Fcancelled," he said.
